# .gitignore for RemakeEngine

### IDE / Editor specific ###
.vscode/
.VSCodeCounter/
.history/

### Godot ###
.godot/
/godot/

### Build artifacts / Dependencies ###
build/
dist/

### Logs ###
*.log
main.log

### Configuration / History ###
config.ini
project.json

### Asset/Texture mapping cache ###
texture_mapping.json
asset_mapping.json
asset_map.sqlite

### Python cache ###
__pycache__/
*.pyc
**/__pycache__/*

### Temporary / Backup / Archived ###
/TMP/
old/
OldModules/
OldRemakeRegistry/
dev/
*.blend1
#uv_map_extract/

# Any directory starting with a dot.
# Be careful with this, it can ignore things like .git if not for other rules.
.*/

### Tools ###
# Note: It's better to not commit tool binaries to the repo.
# scripts are used to download/install them.
/Tools/Blender/blender-4.0.2-windows-x64/
/Tools/Godot/Godot_v4.4.1-stable_mono_win64/
/Tools/QuickBMS/
/Tools/TMP/

### Documentation (external repo) ###
remake-engine-docs/

### Test / Debug / Investigation ###
.test/
test/
investigation_tools/blank.blend
investigation_tools/blank.blend1

### Generated Game Files (RemakeEngine output) ###
/Game/
/GameFiles/
/game/

### Original Game Files (to not be committed) ###
# These are files extracted from the original game.
# To avoid copyright issues, they should not be in the repository.
/Source/
/SourceData/
LightTOC
StreamSetConfig
localereftableD4815ED6.txt
